OL,4,Cin neighbouring room
OL,6,FWhen a young ambulance service trainer
OL,7,Fwas woken by the sound of an alarm,
OL,8,Flittle did he know that a few doors
OL,9,Fdown from his hotel room, a twist of
OL,10,Ffate would save a life.
OL,12,FRory Jones, 26, from Llanrwst, had
OL,13,Ftravelled to Cardiff for a training
OL,14,Fcourse and was staying the night in a
OL,15,Fhotel.
OL,17,FAsleep in his room, he received an
OL,18,Falert on his phone which, despite
OL,19,Fbeing off-duty, had been left on.
