OL,6,FThe alert was from GoodSam, the UK's
OL,7,Fcardiac arrest alerting system. All
OL,8,Fqualified responders can register to
OL,9,Fuse the app, which alerts them to
OL,10,Fnearby cardiac emergencies.
OL,12,FRory soon realised the alert was
OL,13,Fcoming from a neighbouring hotel room,
OL,14,Fand he quickly went to help.
OL,16,FHe said: "When I got to the room, I
OL,17,Fsaw a little girl of about four or
OL,18,Ffive years old lying on the floor and
OL,19,Fher parents were on the phone to the
OL,20,Fambulance service.
