OL,3,CHotel guest saves life of young girl
OL,4,Cin neighbouring room
OL,6,F"I assessed her and noticed she wasn't
OL,7,Fbreathing, so I immediately began CPR
OL,8,Fand started delivering rescue breaths.
OL,9,FThankfully, after one round of CPR she
OL,10,Fstarted breathing again."
OL,12,FRory stayed with the girl and her
OL,13,Ffamily until the ambulance arrived.
OL,15,FHe said: "I completed the assessment
OL,16,Fwith the emergency call handler and
OL,17,Falthough I was confident in what I was
OL,18,Fdoing, it was great to have that
OL,19,Freassuring voice on the phone."
