OL,6,FRory later found out the girl had
OL,7,Freturned home safely from the hospital.
OL,9,FRory first joined St John Ambulance
OL,10,FCymru in March 2022 with no formal
OL,11,Ftraining but is now qualified to teach
OL,12,Fa range of first aid courses as a
OL,13,Ftrainer.
OL,15,FHe said: "It was the first time I've
OL,16,Fperformed CPR on a child in a real-
OL,17,Flife scenario, but within a few days
OL,18,Fof the incident I was teaching other
OL,19,Fpeople how to do it.
