OL,6,F"I would recommend this training for
OL,7,Fanyone who works with or volunteers
OL,8,Fwith children, whether it's a football
OL,9,Fclub or similar group, as paediatric
OL,10,Ffirst aid is a bit different."
OL,12,FRory is hoping to go to university in
OL,13,FSeptember to study paramedic science.
OL,15,FHe also highlighted the importance of
OL,16,Fvolunteering for the GoodSAM alerting
OL,17,Fsystem.
