OL,6,FHe said: "GoodSAM helps reduce
OL,7,Fpressure on the ambulance service and
OL,8,Fis a great first port of call as every
OL,9,Fminute counts, especially when it
OL,10,Fcomes to cardiac or respiratory
OL,11,Farrest. Every minute reduces a child's
OL,12,Fchances of survival by 10%.
OL,14,F"You don't have to have a PHD in CPR,
OL,15,Fanyone can learn and I'd encourage
OL,16,Fanyone that has the relevant training
OL,17,Fto sign-up to GoodSAM."
